# Docker for Node/npm

This project uses Svelte 5 and requires Node 22+. The host shell may have Node 10.x.

**Never run `node`, `npm`, or `npx` on the host** for `web_app/`. Always use Docker from the repo root:

- `docker-compose run --rm chem npm install`
- `docker-compose run --rm chem npm run build`
- `docker-compose run --rm chem npm run <script>` (including tests when added)
- `docker-compose up` for dev

See `.cursor/skills/docker-node/SKILL.md` for full workflow and fallback commands.
